description:
Akitsuki Fuuka is the protagonist of Fuuka, the latest work of the mangaka of Kimi Iru no Machi, http://anidb.net/cr10802 [Seo Kouji].
She is the daughter of http://anidb.net/character/10206 [Suzuka Asahina] from the anime series http://anidb.net/anime/3203 [Suzuka].
name: Akitsuki Fuuka
